snippet.textDisplay: You want to destroy an old classic melody song, give that to coke studio. I know many people will get offended by this but guys just think of it for a moment. " Chandni raten" sang by Noor jahan does not deserve to be treated like this pile of meh, neither does the song "AYA LARYIE NI" by mussarat nazir. Only one song which was remade in a better way is "Afreen Afreen". Please stop ruining classic old music. I know remaking a song can lead to a different version of the original song but it never ever mean that you put together two or three old melodies and produce a garbage like this. We have such amazing talent in Pakistan e.g. QB and Momina have breathtaking voices. Please use them wisely and create art not a sh*******t
